snippet.description:

The Marvels takes the honors as the worst film of the year, and quite possibly the worst film in the entire MCU. It's an absurd creation in pretty much all the ways. And it further establishes that Captain Marvel is a villain on par with Thanos.

snippet.title: Ahsoka - The Bad Side of the Force
snippet.description:
Start speaking a new language in 3 weeks with Babbel ðŸŽ‰. Get 60% OFF your subscription during their Black Friday saleâž¡Here: https://go.babbel.com/t?bsc=1200m60-youtube-growingupwithoutborders1-nov-2023&btp=default&utm_term=generic_v1&utm_medium=paidsocial&utm_source=YouTube&utm_content=Influencer..growingupwithoutborders1..USA..YouTube

Ahsoka is finished. Dave Filoni saved Star Wars! Oh, wait, no he didn't. In Part 4, Sabine puts an entire galaxy at risk of Thrawn's return in order that she gets to see Ezra Bridger again, even though they barely have a relationship to speak of. Ahsoka seemingly dies, but doesn't; and Anakin returns, because of course he does.

Part One: https://youtu.be/w8-UOjGxFUQ
Part Two: https://youtu.be/jO6miEBY3Io?si=gCf-B_yF50rzz_JM
Part Three: https://youtu.be/YK_lNO1u7GM?si=mz7tM7Lf8J5AaF-1

Rebels fans may have derived more joy from the show than the general audience. Then again, Ahsoka butchers a whole lot of Star Wars: Rebels lore as well, so... maybe not.

In order to avoid protracted copyright battles, I'll be releasing this review episode-by-episode across the next couple of weeks.

Thanks to @Loftipixels and@MrBrownAlliance for their help with this video!

snippet.title: Ahsoka - Space Whales and Other Nonsense
snippet.description:
Part One: https://youtu.be/w8-UOjGxFUQ
Part Two: https://youtu.be/jO6miEBY3Io?si=gCf-B_yF50rzz_JM

Ahsoka is finished. Dave Filoni saved Star Wars! Oh, wait, no he didn't. Ahsoka was completely unapproachable to the general audience and at times lapsed into Mandalorian-style awfulness.

Rebels fans may have derived more joy from the show than the general audience. Then again, Ahsoka butchers a whole lot of Star Wars: Rebels lore as well, so... maybe not.

In order to avoid protracted copyright battles, I'll be releasing this review episode-by-episode across the next couple of weeks.

Thanks to @Iambagface and@MrBrownAlliance for their help with this video!
